defaultI would like to thank you for inviting me to speak to the Energy &amp;
default Climate Change Committee on Tuesday. I hope you found the information that my officials and I provided helpful. I recognise that on a number of occasions, we could not give you answers in full and undertook to write to you. Having gone through the officia
